    "body": "@khidesha I can only answer the same thing as above. The gas estimator will work, but if the contract changes state, and your tx is included a few blocks later, the estimated gas might be off. It's generally useful to add a bit of slack to the estimated gas (say 10%) so that small variations don't result in reverts.",
